original_title: Cletus and Clyde: Missing In Possible
overview: Cletus (Sandoval) and Clyde (Fukui) face a new threat when a villainous cyborg (Coelho) threatens to destroy their world. The situation becomes even more complicated when they discover he has villainous partners. Will Cletus and Clyde be able to save the world? Will they be able to save themselves? Find out in this motherfacking action-packed cowboy buddy adventure!
title: Cletus and Clyde: Missing In Possible
